partnerDetails.about: Frontline Electrical Suppliers, owned and managed by Barry and Joanne Bamberger, is situated in Victoria Road, Somerset West just off the N2. Since our business was founded in 1997, we have built a great reputation for ourselves, offering electrical solutions to all our customers for over 18 years.
